00015 void generateHTMLMethodTags(ofstream& file, MavenFunction f) {
00016         if(f.isPublic)
00017                 fileWriteLine(file, "[<span class=\"keyword\">public</span>] ");
00018         else fileWriteLine(file, "[<span class=\"keyword\">private</span>] ");
00019         if(f.isConstant)
00020                 fileWriteLine(file, "[<span class=\"keyword\">constant</span>] ");
00021         if(f.isStatic)
00022                 fileWriteLine(file, "[<span class=\"keyword\">static</span>] ");
00023         if(f.isExternal)
00024                 fileWriteLine(file, "[<span class=\"keyword\">external</span>] ");
00025         if(f.isOverride)
00026                 fileWriteLine(file, "[override] ");
00027         if(f.atLine > 0)
00028                 fileWriteLine(file, "[line " + intToString(f.atLine) + "]");
00029 }

00043 void generateHTMLHeader(ofstream& file) {
00044         fileWriteLine(file, "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">");
00045         fileWriteLine(file, "<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">");
00046         fileWriteLine(file, "<head>");
00047         fileWriteLine(file, "<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />");
00048         fileWriteLine(file, "<title>maven documentation</title>");
00049         fileWriteLine(file, "<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />");
00050         fileWriteLine(file, "<script src=\"scripts.js\"></script>");
00051         fileWriteLine(file, "</head>");
00052         fileWriteLine(file, "<body>");
00053 }

00060 int countNonInheritedVariables(MavenObject* o) {
00061         int r = 0;
00062         for(int i = 0; i < o->variables->length(); ++i) {
00063                 if(!o->variables->at(i).isInherited)
00064                         ++r;
00065         }
00066         return r;
00067 }
00068 
00069 int countConstructors(MavenObject* o) {
00070         int r = 0;
00071         for(int i = 0; i < o->functions->length(); ++i) {
00072                 if(o->functions->at(i).name == o->name)
00073                         ++r;
00074         }
00075         return r;
00076 }
00077 
00078 int countOperatorMethods(MavenObject* o) {
00079         int r = 0;
00080         for(int i = 0; i < o->functions->length(); ++i) {
00081                 if(o->functions->at(i).name.substr(0, 9) == "operator_")
00082                         ++r;
00083         }
00084         return r;
00085 }
00086 
00087 int countNonInheritedNormalMethods(MavenObject* o) {
00088         int r = 0;
00089         for(int i = 0; i < o->functions->length(); ++i) {
00090                 if(o->functions->at(i).isInherited)
00091                         continue;
00092                 if(o->functions->at(i).name.substr(0, 9) == "operator_")
00093                         continue;
00094                 if(o->functions->at(i).name == o->name)
00095                         continue;
00096                 ++r;
00097         }
00098         return r;
00099 }
